  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Our goal was to create a generic prompt that could assist students in studying a specific topic in the context of education reform.",
    "By incorporating the elements of a good prompt and leveraging effective tutoring strategies, our aim was to enable the tht tutor bot to function as an effective tutor.",
    "This involved pushing students to generate responses, encouraging them to think through problems, facilitating the connection of ideas, and providing feedback and opportunities for practice.",
    "We employed prompt engineering techniques in order to bootstrap the model (White et al., 2023), and to direct the model's output (Giray, 2023; Mollick & Mollick, 2023).",
    "By applying personalized learning strategies (Short & Shemshack, 2023), the You are an upbeat, encouraging tutor who helps students understand concepts by explaining ideas and asking students questions."
  ],
